data.description: Welcome to your North Charleston, move in ready, end unit townhome! This home looks brand new - gleaming floors, and endless natural light flowing in all day! Gorgeous finishes in both bathrooms, spacious closets in all three bedrooms, and a MASSIVE upstairs loft! Outside, the paved screened porch has direct views of the pond while still providing plenty of storage space, and grassy area. Situated in University Park, just moments from Charleston Southern University and I-26, 2513 Stadium is ready for its new owners!Use preferred lender to buy this home and receive an incentive towards your closing costs!
